text: Frotey-lès-Vesoul (, literally Frotey near Vesoul) is a commune in the Haute- Saône department in the Bourgogne-Franche-Comté region in east France. The town is near Vesoul. == Related pages == * Communes of the Haute-Saône department == References == == Other websites == * Category:Communes in Haute- Saône
